/*AND*(DLKEYD*LIKE*'Unauth%'*OR*DLKEYD*=*'BatchesNotAccepted'******************/:  BUG28109 MD020661
/*OR*DLKEYD*LIKE*'Unrep%')******************************************************/ BUG28109 AR1042967
/*OR*DLKEYD*LIKE*'Unrep%'*OR*DLKEYD*=*'CorectBatchNotAceptd')******************/:   AR1042967 CCB023
/*OR*DLKEYD*LIKE*'Unrep%'*OR DLKEYD*=*'CorectBatchNotAceptd'********************/    CCB023 MD020661
/*OR*DLKEYD*LIKE*'Wait%')******************************************************/:    CCB023 MD020661
